 struct lnode star head and struct lnode star tail. And if we end up with a linked list of three things,

00:09:55.960 --> 00:10:00.960
 head points to the first item in the list and then within that, there is the text.

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:07.960
 The text points to some string. In this case, it's the letter C. And then the next is an address of the second thing in the list.

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:12.960
 In that second thing, text points to is and next points to the third thing in the list.

